板料锯切机和剪切机械

sentences.sentence: As soon as the lights were out, these untiring nibblers set to work.
sentences.translation: 灯火一熄，这些不知疲倦的爱咬东西的家伙就开始闹将起来。

sentences.sentence: Christ wants not nibblers at the possible, but grabbers of the impossible.
sentences.translation: 基督要的不是面对可能事物的浅尝辄止，而是面对不可能时的刚毅果断。

sentences.sentence: This was blamed on the rabbits, for it is well known that carrot-nibblers with long ear cause floods.
sentences.translation: 责任怪罪到兔子头上,因为众所周知,长耳朵并小口小口吃 胡萝卜的动物会引起洪水。
